question: Which among the following statement is not correct?
option1: First man to step onto the Moon was American
option2: First man to orbit the earth was a Russian
option3: First man to voyage around Cape of Good Hope was a Portuguese
option4: First man to Discover New Zealand was a Portuguese
answer: First man to Discover New Zealand was a Portuguese
explanation: First man to Discover New Zealand & Tasmania was Abel Janszoon and he was a Dutch.
